<body>
<div class="enquiry">
    <div class="container3">
        <div class="form-left">
            <h2>Enquiry Form</h2>
            <p>We are here to provide transparent, seamless, and informative care. Whether you need medical equipment, nursing/elder care, doctor consultation, or lab tests, reach out to us with any queries. Follow these steps to submit your enquiry:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Step 1 - Select Enquiry Type: Choose the service you are interested in.</li>
                <li>Step 2 - Enter your contact details - Name, Email ID & Phone no</li>
                <li>Step 3 - Your Question: Provide details about your query.</li>
                <li>Step 4 - Preferred Contact Time: Let us know your preferred time for us to contact you.</li>
                <li>Step 5 - Submit: Click the submit button to send your request to our team.</li>
            <p>Our team will get in touch with you shortly to assist with your needs.</p>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="form-right">
            <h3>Please select one of the below:</h3>
            <div class="button-group">
                <button class="active" data-form="enquiry">Enquiry</button>
            </div>
            <form id="enquiry-form" class="form-content active">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="enquiry-type">Enquiry Type</label>
                    <select id="enquiry-type" name ="enquiry_type">
                        <option value="">- Select -</option>
                        <option value="nursing-care">Nursing Care</option>
                        <option value="elder-care">Elder Care</option>
                        <option value="doctor-consultation">Doctor Consultation</option>
                        <option value="buy-rent-medical-equipment">Buy/Rent Medical Equipment</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email ID</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email ID">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter Name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="mobile">Mobile No.</label>
                    <input type="text" id="mobile" name="mobile" placeholder="Enter Mobile No.">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="time">Preferred Time To Call</label>
                    <select id="time" name="preferred_time">
                        <option value="">- Select -</option>
                        <option value="08:00-09:00">08:00 AM - 09:00 AM</option>
                        <option value="09:00-10:00">09:00 AM - 10:00 AM</option>
                        <option value="10:00-11:00">10:00 AM - 11:00 AM</option>
                        <option value="11:00-12:00">11:00 AM - 12:00 PM</option>
                        <option value="12:00-13:00">12:00 PM - 01:00 PM</option>
                        <option value="13:00-14:00">01:00 PM - 02:00 PM</option>
                        <option value="14:00-15:00">02:00 PM - 03:00 PM</option>
                        <option value="15:00-16:00">03:00 PM - 04:00 PM</option>
                        <option value="16:00-17:00">04:00 PM - 05:00 PM</option>
                        <option value="17:00-18:00">05:00 PM - 06:00 PM</option>
                        <option value="18:00-19:00">06:00 PM - 07:00 PM</option>
                        <option value="19:00-20:00">07:00 PM - 08:00 PM</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="remark">Remark</label>
                    <textarea id="remark" name="remark" placeholder="Please enter remark here"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="submit">
                    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </form>

            <form id="feedback-form" class="form-content">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="feedback-email">Email ID</label>
                    <input type="email" id="feedback-email" name="email" placeholder="Email ID">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="feedback-name">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="feedback-name" name="name" placeholder="Enter Name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="feedback-comments">Comments</label>
                    <textarea id="feedback-comments" name="comments" placeholder="Enter your comments"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="submit">
                    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        <!-- <div class="contact-info">
            <button>+91 987654321</button>
        </div> -->
    </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.emailjs.com/dist/email.min.js"></script>
